items.sentence: I'm sure that Tom will think that we shouldn't do that.
Do you think that things like that don't really matter?
That old man had been making moonshine for fifty years.
Tom hasn't been here since the last time you were here.
Tom and Mary will be coming to the party by themselves.
All I want you to do is sit there and not say anything.
There was a man sitting on that bench not too long ago.
You should've told me that you wanted me to come alone.
Tom has been working in Australia for over three years.
Tom told me that he'd give me that book if I wanted it.
